Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.29,0:01:44.77,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,痛 痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.37,0:01:47.37,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,擦傷 幸運
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.34,0:01:49.04,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,芙蕾多妮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.18,0:01:51.43,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,芙蕾多妮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.31,0:01:56.21,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,回答 請求
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.91,0:02:01.87,Default,Fredrica,0,0,0,,討厭 這島怎麼回事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.47,0:02:11.28,Default,Fredrica,0,0,0,,嘉依卡掉哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.32,0:02:23.00,Default,David,0,0,0,,沒受傷吧 大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.00,0:02:24.29,Default,Red,0,0,0,,肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.29,0:02:27.21,Default,David,0,0,0,,看來咱飄到要找的島了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.21,0:02:30.83,Default,Selma,0,0,0,,那團霧 應該是魔法做出來隱藏小島的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.79,0:02:33.42,Default,Selma,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.42,0:02:34.12,Default,Red,0,0,0,,負傷？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.12,0:02:38.05,Default,David,0,0,0,,嗯 被船的碎片傷到了 真倒霉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.05,0:02:42.30,Default,David,0,0,0,,快點上島吧 免得剛才那怪物回來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.98,0:03:01.07,Default,David,0,0,0,,在擔心亂破師小哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.07,0:03:02.60,Default,Red,0,0,0,,否…否定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.60,0:03:05.90,Default,David,0,0,0,,不用擔心 這點小事他死不了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.58,0:03:14.42,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,這情況下魔法還真方便
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:18.32,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,同感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.32,0:03:20.55,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,要不是兄長跟嘉依卡吵架 這會兒應該已經到頂了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.00,0:03:22.47,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,這是在挖苦我？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.47,0:03:25.06,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,我怎麼會挖苦敬愛的兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.06,0:03:30.14,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,不過 如果兄長有被言語侮辱的性癖 我樂意效勞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:31.64,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,閉嘴快爬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.25,0:03:45.13,Default,Orthros,0,0,0,,Herukerun... Unzerun... Korukerun... Peie... Sebue...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.57,0:03:54.33,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,雙頭犬…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.33,0:03:56.81,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,Els, nyme, ainkt, mu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.54,0:03:59.71,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,顯現吧 光煌之物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.71,0:04:01.22,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,【閃耀者】
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:27.78,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,入侵者 逮捕 帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.89,0:04:30.69,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,這座島 居民？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.29,0:04:34.19,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,我 這座島知道 請求
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.53,0:04:37.45,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,入侵者 逮捕 帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.96,0:04:45.30,Default,David,0,0,0,,島是找到了 可之後該幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:47.97,Default,Selma,0,0,0,,奇伊說來了就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.07,0:04:53.43,Default,Red,0,0,0,,什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.57,0:04:58.13,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,這玩意…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.13,0:04:59.66,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,是嘉依卡的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.66,0:05:02.15,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,看來確實來這邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.27,0:05:04.05,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.05,0:05:04.65,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.47,0:05:11.95,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,亞人兵…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:14.22,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,他們是這島的警衛？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.22,0:05:15.14,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,像是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.14,0:05:18.92,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,他們會在這裏晃悠 證明肯定有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.92,0:05:23.47,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,如果嘉依卡也在這 可能已經被他們抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.47,0:05:28.11,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,我去跟蹤他們 阿卡莉在樹林裏找找
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.11,0:05:28.93,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.30,0:05:38.63,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,島的地下 巨大設施
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.70,0:05:42.09,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,父親的遺產 存在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.73,0:05:52.84,Default,Wizard,0,0,0,,伊茨瑪希大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.04,0:05:55.54,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,棄獸們幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.57,0:06:00.64,Default,Wizard,0,0,0,,是 目前正與亞人兵部隊合作 搜尋入侵者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.84,0:06:02.73,Default,Wizard,0,0,0,,應該很快會有報告
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.51,0:06:12.89,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,觀察過程和記錄數據
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.49,0:06:15.88,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,這種事有什麼意義
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.41,0:06:19.84,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,陛下所求之物早已完成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.29,0:06:25.90,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,但是 知道如何啟動它的 只有賈茲皇帝陛下一人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.89,0:06:28.92,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,我們連線索都沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.71,0:06:31.72,Default,Gaz,0,0,0,,朕命不久矣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.71,0:06:37.49,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,陛下如今已駕崩 這座島還有意義嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:40.28,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,進來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.76,0:06:44.40,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,搜索隊回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.42,0:06:49.21,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,入侵小島的幾人已抓獲 關進地牢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.61,0:06:52.65,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,應該是從附近經過的貨船上的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.55,0:06:54.69,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,要立刻審問嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.09,0:06:56.01,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,不急
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:07:00.62,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,另外 南側懸崖處也有入侵者的蹤跡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.02,0:07:03.58,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,附近搜索過後 沒發現可疑人物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.43,0:07:06.19,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,搜查已暫時中止
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.59,0:07:07.60,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,中止？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.00,0:07:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我說過上島的人要全部抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.66,0:07:12.82,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.22,0:07:16.26,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,但是報告上說 光線太暗路況也很差
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.66,0:07:18.33,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,深追下去搜索隊也會有危險
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.73,0:07:20.56,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,少跟我頂嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:26.52,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,是我打發慈悲 啟用你們這些走投無路的戰爭的遺留品
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.92,0:07:29.71,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,你們這些亞人按吩咐辦事就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.99,0:07:33.84,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.78,0:07:36.86,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,嗯 區區亞人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.26,0:07:39.70,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,量產型數量已成規模
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.10,0:07:43.54,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,小心我拿你們當實驗材料處理掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.37,0:07:53.96,Default,Ursula,0,0,0,,吃飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.78,0:07:55.48,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.23,0:07:58.70,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,我拘捕 為何
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.10,0:08:01.45,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,這座島 秘密 目的 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.38,0:08:04.53,Default,Ursula,0,0,0,,我什麼都不能說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.93,0:08:08.34,Default,Ursula,0,0,0,,上頭的人早晚會來 到時去問他們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.74,0:08:09.70,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.10,0:08:12.86,Default,Wizard,0,0,0,,娥蘇拉 棄獸怎麼還沒喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:14.04,Default,Ursula,0,0,0,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.44,0:08:14.78,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,娥蘇拉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.82,0:08:18.26,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,娥蘇拉 高潔之花？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.66,0:08:20.54,Default,Ursula,0,0,0,,嗯 是拉克語
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.80,0:08:22.74,Default,Ursula,0,0,0,,你懂拉克語？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.14,0:08:25.45,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嗯 出身 賈茲帝國
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.85,0:08:26.21,Default,Ursula,0,0,0,,你也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:27.06,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:27.79,Default,Ursula,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.51,0:08:31.29,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,這座島 研究 賈茲皇帝的命令？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.06,0:08:36.38,Default,Ursula,0,0,0,,抱歉 詳細情況我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:07.17,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,把整座島挖空造出來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.57,0:09:08.96,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,好大的手筆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.73,0:09:23.80,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,又是棄獸？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.73,0:09:35.48,Default,Fredrica,0,0,0,,啊咧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:37.23,Default,Fredrica,0,0,0,,阿卡莉來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.96,0:09:39.76,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,芙蕾多妮卡 嘉依卡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.00,0:09:42.45,Default,Fredrica,0,0,0,,誒 我也在找呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.19,0:09:43.87,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.27,0:09:46.49,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,導讀怎麼回事……這座島
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.41,0:09:55.38,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,推…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.18,0:09:58.88,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,就你一個？芙蕾多妮卡呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:00.69,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,走散
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.09,0:10:01.59,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,先從這裏出去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.46,0:10:06.47,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,有沒有人來 幫我看著點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.83,0:10:09.09,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,托魯 謝罪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.78,0:10:13.96,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,我 不聽勸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.36,0:10:15.15,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,大家 麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.55,0:10:16.58,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.98,0:10:19.49,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,不 我也太急功近利了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.28,0:10:22.19,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,再說島也找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.59,0:10:24.20,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,總之 這事回頭再說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.87,0:10:26.82,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,這島肯定有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.22,0:10:28.37,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,棺材和機仗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.77,0:10:30.38,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,棺材 芙蕾多妮卡拿著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.78,0:10:31.58,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,機仗已沒收
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:33.87,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,機仗先不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.27,0:10:37.89,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,先逃到個安全的地方 再考慮之後的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.29,0:10:38.96,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:47.89,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,裝鎧龍和雙頭犬？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.29,0:10:48.77,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.17,0:10:51.47,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,襲擊船的是大海魔…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.87,0:10:54.67,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,這島上的人 馴養著棄獸？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.39,0:11:00.92,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,這邊不太妙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.32,0:11:02.50,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,找別的出口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.90,0:11:03.32,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.57,0:11:18.25,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,這裏是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.51,0:11:29.93,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,潛下去應該連著外面的大海
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.81,0:11:32.93,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,但根本看不出有多深啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.72,0:11:40.65,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,棄獸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.95,0:11:44.86,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,那不是自然的棄獸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.26,0:11:45.97,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.03,0:11:51.62,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,它們都是復製品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.30,0:12:11.49,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,大海魔…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.91,0:12:22.03,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,剛才是它在說話？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.43,0:12:23.82,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,它能說話？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:27.66,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,大海魔 高智能 等同裝鎧龍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.06,0:12:29.57,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,復製品是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.47,0:12:37.20,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,這設施中 在研究如何用煉生魔法量產棄獸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.60,0:12:41.01,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,扔在這裏的 就是其失敗品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.93,0:12:43.72,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,你也是其中之一？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.12,0:12:46.72,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,我是被抓來做實驗的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.66,0:12:51.10,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,通過研究我的肉體 進行複製
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.13,0:12:54.52,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,誕生了量產型大海魔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:12:59.19,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,待遇 殘酷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.31,0:13:02.50,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,銀色頭髮 紫色瞳孔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.90,0:13:05.57,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,背棺材的公主 嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.49,0:13:08.27,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,你認識嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.67,0:13:12.08,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,我曾遇到過一個自稱嘉依卡的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.48,0:13:16.79,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,她知道了自己的命運 拋棄了嘉依卡之名
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.01,0:13:21.13,Default,Layla,0,0,0,,但某一天 我得知了真相
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.98,0:13:25.75,Default,Layla,0,0,0,,一切只是為收集《遺體》的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.15,0:13:28.05,Default,Layla,0,0,0,,嘉依卡是 幫助嘉依卡的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.15,0:13:30.09,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,蕾拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.49,0:13:31.95,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,她來過這座島？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.35,0:13:33.93,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,我 真相 追尋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.33,0:13:35.56,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嘉依卡 真相 知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.78,0:13:39.34,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,我的生命即將消逝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.74,0:13:44.89,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,你的問題我會如數作答 背棺材的公主啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.29,0:13:48.07,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,我 什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:50.56,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,推動命運的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.96,0:13:56.22,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,帶著剛才 收集遺體 將自身化為道具
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.62,0:13:58.37,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,以開啟命運之鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.77,0:14:00.65,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,命運？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.79,0:14:04.84,Default,Ursula,0,0,0,,我來守餐具時 發現門開著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.72,0:14:07.21,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,有同夥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:09.63,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,估計是搜索隊漏掉的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.03,0:14:12.32,Default,Ursula,0,0,0,,對不起 基裏爾 是我一時疏忽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.72,0:14:13.80,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,這不怪娥蘇拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.57,0:14:16.77,Default,Ursula,0,0,0,,但是 肯定會受罰的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.17,0:14:19.95,Default,Ursula,0,0,0,,因為伊茨瑪希大人討厭我們亞人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.35,0:14:21.29,Default,Ursula,0,0,0,,沒準回事死刑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.69,0:14:22.56,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,這種事他休想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.61,0:14:24.71,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,我馬上抓人回來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.35,0:14:31.39,Default,David,0,0,0,,怎麼 這匆忙勁有點怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.79,0:14:33.00,Default,Selma,0,0,0,,看來是出事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.40,0:14:36.31,Default,David,0,0,0,,運氣好的話 咱們沒準也有機會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.75,0:14:39.16,Default,Selma,0,0,0,,喂 不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.43,0:14:46.90,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,人類所謂的魔法 是將思念具象化的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.30,0:14:49.94,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,遙遠的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.34,0:14:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我們棄獸 從人類誕生之前就與這力量為伴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.56,0:14:59.56,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,後來人類誕生 開始嚮往魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.93,0:15:02.76,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,模仿研究我們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.16,0:15:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,最終借助人工的魔法器具 施展出多彩的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.72,0:15:12.34,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,魔法器具 機仗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.74,0:15:19.33,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,隨後人類的魔法技術 因一位魔法師取得飛躍性發展
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:24.71,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,有<禁断皇帝>之稱的男人 亞爾圖·賈茲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.94,0:15:28.11,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,父親…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.51,0:15:34.09,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,所謂嘉依卡 是賈茲皇帝用來實現胸中宏偉野心的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.49,0:15:38.12,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,他們的生與死 喜悅與哀傷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.52,0:15:42.75,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,都按既定的齒輪而動 無法反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.15,0:15:44.56,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,為什麼 你知道這些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:51.84,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,從太古起我們就與其他個體思維想通 將一切看在眼中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.24,0:15:57.87,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,一旦命運邁出腳步 不止是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.27,0:16:01.20,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,都將會被捲入破壞與殺戮的漩渦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.20,0:16:04.91,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,嘉依卡手握這柄鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.31,0:16:07.40,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,這一點萬不可忘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:13.11,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.98,0:16:16.63,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,嘉依卡 別離我太遠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.03,0:16:17.09,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:25.39,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,別放跑他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.43,0:16:38.78,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,托魯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.79,0:16:41.74,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.97,0:16:46.03,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,嘉依卡 不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.43,0:16:46.71,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.11,0:16:47.69,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.10,0:16:50.13,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,你剛才叫她嘉依卡？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.57,0:16:52.59,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,你是嘉依卡？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.71,0:16:55.34,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,嘉依卡？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.02,0:16:57.88,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.28,0:17:01.57,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,確認之後 發現抓到的另一組入侵者之後也有個相似的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.97,0:17:03.77,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,那邊也自稱嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.82,0:17:06.62,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,兩個嘉依卡同時來…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.58,0:17:08.69,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,這是偶然嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.40,0:17:11.03,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,不 很有錢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.06,0:17:14.15,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,帶到這裏來 兩個一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.76,0:17:17.48,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,城堡？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.88,0:17:20.97,Default,Drunk,0,0,0,,沒錯 飄在天上的大城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.37,0:17:25.33,Default,Drunk,0,0,0,,站在前面山丘上 能很清楚看到國界附近
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.73,0:17:29.29,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,在賈茲帝國國界附近 看到天上飛的城堡了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.69,0:17:30.29,Default,Drunk,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.12,0:17:35.28,Default,Drunk,0,0,0,,在月光下 那麼大個的城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.68,0:17:39.26,Default,Drunk,0,0,0,,還一次出來五六個 給我都嚇傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.07,0:17:41.33,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,五六個？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.73,0:17:45.12,Default,Drunk,0,0,0,,而且到了早晨 就像煙一樣消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.52,0:17:46.52,Default,Zita,0,0,0,,什麼時候的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.25,0:17:48.89,Default,Drunk,0,0,0,,是我還小的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.29,0:17:52.38,Default,Drunk,0,0,0,,80年…不 90年前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.78,0:17:53.18,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.58,0:17:56.56,Default,Zita,0,0,0,,是什麼形狀 能畫在這上面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.12,0:18:01.81,Default,Zita,0,0,0,,看著像航天要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.21,0:18:04.16,Default,Leo,0,0,0,,賈茲帝國裏飄著航天要塞？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.35,0:18:09.34,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,繞道國界附近 本想找找遺產的傳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.74,0:18:11.62,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,結果聽到個怪事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.46,0:18:16.74,Default,Matheus,0,0,0,,但是 那個時代應該還沒發明出航天要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.14,0:18:19.88,Default,Leo,0,0,0,,跟皇帝的遺產貌似沒什麼關係啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.28,0:18:22.88,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,不好下結論
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.28,0:18:26.95,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,遺產 航天要塞 還有嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.21,0:18:31.10,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,賈茲皇帝究竟想留下什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.42,0:18:34.91,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,伊茨瑪希大人 帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.79,0:18:49.37,Default,Red,0,0,0,,接觸 拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.04,0:18:51.08,Default,Red,0,0,0,,無禮之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.07,0:18:52.83,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,又見面了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.44,0:19:01.73,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.13,0:19:04.61,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,並排一站果然很相像
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.01,0:19:07.20,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,歡迎 嘉依卡·賈茲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.60,0:19:11.85,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,我是賈茲帝國魔法技術員副院長 維克多·伊茨瑪希
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.13,0:19:14.93,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,魔法技術院？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.33,0:19:16.10,Default,Niva,0,0,0,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.24,0:19:18.19,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,有反應了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.61,0:19:20.48,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.15,0:19:22.21,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,啊 我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.61,0:19:25.78,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,上次嘉依卡來時還在開發之中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.18,0:19:27.82,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,那麼果然嘉依卡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.22,0:19:28.78,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,上次？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.18,0:19:29.91,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,蕾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.73,0:19:33.62,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,太棒了 收穫超出預期
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.66,0:19:37.96,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,你們來這裏也在賈茲皇帝計劃之中嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.19,0:19:41.31,Default,Red,0,0,0,,你 父親的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.71,0:19:42.92,Default,Red,0,0,0,,我 皇帝的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.32,0:19:45.23,Default,Red,0,0,0,,捆縛 監禁 無禮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.43,0:19:52.40,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,女兒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.42,0:19:53.85,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,聽好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.70,0:19:57.35,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,賈茲皇帝可沒有女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.86,0:19:59.86,Default,Red,0,0,0,,一…一派胡言
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.48,0:20:05.11,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,戰後 街頭巷尾滿是戰爭孤兒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.15,0:20:12.29,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,計劃書中寫道【從其中秘選一批同齡女孩】
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:15.36,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,【對記憶進行了魔法處理】
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.37,0:20:26.54,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,在所有女孩腦中 加入了同一份賈茲皇帝女兒的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.79,0:20:30.43,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,這就是嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.40,0:20:37.73,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,覺醒的嘉依卡會準備好棺材 開始收集皇帝陛下的遺體
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.52,0:20:43.07,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,不過收集的理由會因個體不同
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.87,0:20:47.49,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,就是它 證據不就在這嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.89,0:20:50.03,Default,Red,0,0,0,,否定 否定 否定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.70,0:20:56.92,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,所謂嘉依卡 是賈茲皇帝用來實現胸中宏偉野心的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.14,0:21:01.79,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,他們的生與死 喜悅與哀傷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.19,0:21:06.38,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,都按既定的齒輪而動 無法反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.78,0:21:08.37,Default,Layla,0,0,0,,你還不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.77,0:21:11.00,Default,Layla,0,0,0,,自己為何而活 因何而生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.40,0:21:18.64,Default,Layla,0,0,0,,當知道這些時 你會從心底絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.89,0:21:21.15,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.39,0:21:26.36,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,捏造的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.07,0:21:28.94,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,真是來得太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.34,0:21:31.32,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,這下研究也會大幅進展
